 ('1', '12', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Orangina refreshed their brand identity Achtung!/Kraftwerk wastasked to extend their newbrand identity to a fresh online experience. ', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, 'big', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', '2016-02-26 10:46:08', '2016-03-16 21:07:07', '9d09384c-6dde-46b8-bc11-280ecfd90561'),
 ('2', '14', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-02-26 11:34:33', '2016-03-16 21:07:07', '9a32a5d3-040e-4261-9dce-f7f7cb9ddcaf'),
 ('3', '17', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Strategy, Concept & UX', 'The content of the new Orangina website was meantto be kept simple serving a few main purposes.', 'In general there were two main obectives, informing people about the available range of Orangina products and telling them about the history of Orangina as a brand. The homepage would then serve as a hub to these two objectives, as well as to the Orangina social channels.', '#fdaa31', NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, '2016-02-26 13:29:08', '2016-03-16 21:07:08', 'fbd00b0a-afbb-480c-8dfc-2af114fa5dbd'),
 ('4', '19', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#ffa600', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-02-26 13:53:26', '2016-03-16 21:07:08', '5f04cbfa-691a-4dbf-938d-2cec2d65d4c1'),
 ('5', '20', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Design elements', 'Colors for the Orangina website were besides the brand’s Blue and Yellow, based on the labels of the different flavours. ', '', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'big', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, '2016-02-26 14:02:48', '2016-03-16 21:07:08', '940efd6c-e536-4690-805e-78e47b133327'),
 ('6', '22', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-02-26 14:08:10', '2016-03-16 21:07:08', '4ac5c5e9-72e5-405e-8e59-9c8d996b6af0'),
 ('7', '23', 'en_us', 'Iconography', 'To add on the playfull, quirky identity of Orangina, we created an iconset that was used throughout the website.', 'Our hands on mentality can be found throughout the whole process. We bring ideas to life early. We prototype to keep improving along the way. ', '#ffffff', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, 'small', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-02-26 14:13:03', '2016-03-16 21:07:08', '00cc44c8-71e5-44dd-9b76-ec8970af2308'),
 ('8', '25', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Final Designs', 'The content of the new Orangina website was meantto be kept simple serving a few main purposes.', 'In general there were two main obectives, informing people about the available range of Orangina products and telling them about the history of Orangina as a brand. The homepage would then serve as a hub to these two objectives, as well as to the Orangina social channels.', '#092865', NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'big', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, '2016-02-29 09:37:51', '2016-03-16 21:07:08', 'a9daad8f-5572-4053-a90f-701e74df278f'),
 ('9', '29', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#092865', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-02-29 09:41:30', '2016-03-16 21:07:08', '51d70b8e-83e4-424e-920a-2cd4be855f5f'),
 ('12', '80', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A website that let’s fans share their love for Chocomel, seamlessly integrated with a delicious product showcase.', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, 'big', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', '2016-03-16 15:28:59', '2016-03-17 00:27:11', 'faf260b0-95a5-4a62-b47b-ee0ea1107b56'),
 ('13', '81', 'en_us', 'Designing for a love brand', 'When we were asked to design the brand portal for Chocomel we knew it was about chocolate love. A lot of loyal fans have a healthy obsession for this tasty chocolate drink.', 'Chocomel wanted to position themselves as an A-brand bevarage along with the common soft drinks. Their previous image was more cozy and soft. The new image on the otherhand was to be more fashionable and exclusive.', '#391f12', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, 'big', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 15:28:59', '2016-03-17 00:27:11', 'fbb4c01a-dce6-40c8-b03b-2605d901d98b'),
 ('14', '83', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'big', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 15:33:25', '2016-03-17 00:27:11', '17b736ea-105e-4688-8b83-09574c1cad2e'),
 ('15', '86', 'en_us', 'The voice of chocomel lovers', 'Instead of Chocomel telling visitors how great Chocomel really is, we engaged the already big group of fans and let them speak for the brand.', 'In a mix of owned and shared content, the homepage is build up from quotes on twitter, fanphoto’s on instagram and video’s on youtube.', '#f0e9e4', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#391f10', NULL, NULL, 'none', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 15:46:55', '2016-03-17 00:27:11', '4502ba85-9b22-45c4-873e-a0ff7907b663'),
 ('16', '89', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Enjoying your Chocomel hot or cold?', 'Winter or summer, Chocomel can be consumed\r\nboth hot and cold. ', 'Depending on the season, we present the hero product in a warm mug or a cold glass. Since there is an ever lasting discussion on how Chocomel should be consumed, we gave users the option to switch.', '#391f12', NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'big', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, '2016-03-16 15:54:54', '2016-03-17 00:27:11', '58ceab7e-d5da-4da7-8ca7-b5a17ee6751f'),
 ('17', '90', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'white', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 15:54:54', '2016-03-17 00:27:11', 'f8fe58f2-8383-49b3-b935-c6c7731c7c39'),
 ('18', '91', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Life sized photography', 'When it comes to the product, we let the iconic photography speak.', 'In a colorful design, we showed visitors life size photography of the iconic Chocomel pack paired with a hot mug or a cool glass. The product pages has all the key information visitors want to know about their drink: nutritional information, ingrediënts, pack sizes and tell about the durable chocolate that is used in the drink.', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'small', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, '2016-03-16 16:47:03', '2016-03-17 00:27:11', 'c91180b6-0f74-4e9b-a673-126bc061460b'),
 ('19', '93', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'small', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 16:53:30', '2016-03-17 00:27:11', '33b6f29c-8974-4040-938c-b2ca0c2160ed'),
 ('20', '101', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A site that looks sharp  accross every screen', 'The grid view helps when scaling the website, by defining the number of horizontal columns the site looks great across all devices and screens. ', 'Massive screens gets a 5 column grid while small screens like phone get a modified 2 columns grid. ', '#f0e9e4', NULL, NULL, '#3b1f10', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'big', 'small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, '2016-03-17 00:25:22', '2016-03-17 00:27:11', '27ac5317-3fa1-4599-873a-b444f9cd836b'),
 ('21', '102', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#f0e9e4', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'small', 'big', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-17 00:25:22', '2016-03-17 00:27:11', 'e3543a97-5ddb-4c54-ab6f-7f1cf1377caf');



